      "title": "CID interrogates Johnston for 4 hours",
      "body_lines": [
        "The CID has questioned former Minister Joston Fernando today (24) for nearly 4 hours and recorded a statement regarding the incident that took place in front of Temple Trees and at the Galle Face on May 09.",
        "According to a notice issued by the CID. Mr. Johnston Fernando had arrived at the CID at 9.30 am today and obtained his statement until 1.00 pm."
